"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rubick_magic_duel_Description"	"Rubick forcibly duels an enemy hero for a brief duration. During the duel, both heroes can only cast spells and cannot attack or use any items. If a hero dies during the duel, the winner permanently gains a spell amplification.\nWinning a duel against neutral creeps also grants a reward, but only once per round.\nSpell Amplification rewards do not apply to percentage-based abilities."
